author: jalkanen
msg: Enhanced makeLink() to handle most link types (EMPTY, LOCALREF, LOCAL, EXTERNAL, IMAGE).
EMPTY links are now just underlined. No page reference is generated.
Links to WikiNames are now encoded with WikiEngine.encodeName() before
going to the output.  This allows arbitrary WikiNames.
